Class ConfigurationSave

java.lang.Object
model.ConfigurationSave
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class ConfigurationSave extends Object implements Serializable
Serializable class representing a configuration for email sending. Contains various settings such as server configuration, file paths, email content, and indices.
